msContents.summary: A document of the Curia Romana, the "relatione" probably deals with the court of Sixtus V; index mentions Cardinals Diaconi, Vescovi, and Preti, among others. Bound with Raccolta d'alcuni avvertimenti politici di Monsignore [Marsilio?] Landriani [legate to France, 1591?].

msItem.title: Sommaria relatione et breve avviso della gran corte di Roma solo per istruttione di nuovo cardinale
Introduction, index, and poem, f. i recto
Raccolta d'alcuni avvertimenti politici di Monsig[nore] Landriani, f. 86r [=85r]

supportDesc.extent: 154 leaves : 271 x 201 (202 x 120) mm. bound to 277 x 204 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 154; iv, 1-70, 72-150, 153; contemporary foliation in ink, upper right recto. Unnumbered folio between 85 and 86 missing, with loss of text. Numbered folios 71, 151, and 152 missing, with no loss of text.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by two different hands, with the final folio in a third hand.

binding.p: Contemporary vellum with remnants of leather ties; lower cover torn.

history.provenance: Formerly owned by Antonio Ubaldini (signature, inside lower cover).
